<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201019/1ce5eb0fbf0f488199d4407c7e021b59.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>开门见山，这期节目就是要好好跟大伙<strong>说说轮胎的那些个“猫腻”事儿</strong>。老话常说“新三年旧三年，缝缝补补又三年”衣服能将就，可是这<strong>关乎安全的轮胎咱真的不能将就啊~</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=219518351&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
